1.Install Docker for windows

Prepare soure code and kubernete manifest file.yaml

2.Local test
docker-compose up -d

docker images 

docker ps

docker-compose donw


3.Push to Registry

docker Tag <name> Registry/<name>:v1

docker push Registry/<name>:v1


4.Run app

docker apply -f  file.yaml 

kubectl get service

kubectl ger pod

5.scale
kubectl scale --replicas=5 deployment/<name>



